CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 29, 1962, pg. 20, reads: "Limbo, Everybody! - ...at the annual Christmas party of the American Woodmen. Limbo and twisting highlighted the afternoon of Christmas activities."Names on chart include:  I. Robinson, Lottie Luby, J. pg. Black, J. D. Barnett, Roland T. Myers, T. Robert Simpson, Robert Mahaffey?, Josephine Moreland, and Rosa L. Carter.
TitMainTitle: Girls and boys standing around table with three men and woman on other side handing out wrapped candy, at Christmas party sponsored by American Woodmen
